{"tid":1368623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不入村，不挑釁，保護手足，一齊黎，一齊走","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:19:23.000Z","uid":127451,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b9034142fcdba92f0789531436df6e5a77200b08","tid":1368623,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"聽日，一定會有班人不惜一段去挑釁，甚至可能會煽動大家既情緒，目的要大家出手。大家要保持理性，遇上挑釁可以唱sing hallelujah to the lord，遇到對方郁手，以人數優勢制服對方，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以最低武力處理</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n請各位手足，不論係和理非定勇武，要保護自己，保護同路人，不要意氣用事，唔好入村。唔想再見到有手捉受傷，被捕。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油。"},{"pid":"c360edb378a1849d951cbf83d118df2138587a8f","tid":1368623,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3801ee087e1380be230a947b2fee7dc39a7ae20b","tid":1368623,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"dfc6c1feda2cdcecc8742b851a52585a0b0f80ff","tid":1368623,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c772d4318a4fd967adf3b0ccb02a187d1d7374aa","tid":1368623,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"張建宗神助攻，其實聽日唔去遊行，班友自己都會狗咬狗<br />\n聽日入元朗既，行下街食下野唔駛動氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82660c9ce49dab22c2dc33b24c188ad207df7bf2","tid":1368623,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"岩 只需要制服對家 制服黑社會完全冇問題!!"},{"pid":"653edd04affe4e16b2464e8fb1937020b316805b","tid":1368623,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cad60a0e676e6e905eb358ddefd68ce93bef797","tid":1368623,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"340c730eb5